(10, 10, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 'uploads/custom-images/blogs/image-2024-05-20-05-17-01-5165.jpg', 'What Makes the University of Essex Stand Out?', '<div><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">The University of Essex welcomes students from over 140 nations, offering a premier destination for those seeking a transformative study abroad experience in the UK. Nestled in the historic city of Colchester, with a legacy spanning over 2,000 years, our stunning 200-acre campus blends modernity with academic excellence and vibrant social amenities.</span><br></div><div><br></div><div>Explore below to uncover what makes the University of Essex a global hub of learning and discovery, attracting students from around the world.</div><div><br></div><div><b>1. **Exceptional Location**&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp;Immerse yourself in history and natural splendor within Essex\'s picturesque landscapes. Surrounding the campus are quaint English towns, ancient Roman ruins, and 550 kilometers of stunning coastline. Indulge in fresh seafood and vibrant nightlife in Southend, home to the world\'s longest pleasure pier. With London just an hour away by train, the allure of the capital is within easy reach for day trips or weekend escapades.</div><div><br></div><div><b>2. **Diverse International Community**&nbsp;&nbsp;</b></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp;Transitioning to life in the UK is seamless at Essex, thanks to our vibrant international community comprising 16,000 students from over 140 countries. Find your social circle effortlessly among our diverse student body. Explore over 165 student societies, ranging from anime enthusiasts to meditation groups, fostering connections and passions alike.</div><div><br></div><div><b>3. **Comprehensive Student Support**&nbsp;&nbsp;</b></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp;Your well-being and success are paramount at Essex. Access a range of support services tailored to international students, including mental health support, career guidance, and academic workshops. Our personalized personal tutor system empowers you to become an independent thinker, fostering critical analysis and self-directed learning.</div><div><br></div><div><b>4. **Academic Excellence**&nbsp;&nbsp;</b></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp;Ranked among the top 40 universities in the UK overall, Essex delivers a rigorous higher education experience that cultivates critical thinking and professional readiness. Recognized for teaching effectiveness, our faculty invest in your academic journey, offering personalized support and innovative teaching methodologies.</div><div><b><br></b></div><div><b>5. **Superb Campus Facilities**&nbsp;&nbsp;</b></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp;Experience unparalleled campus life with an array of leisure and learning facilities at your disposal. From shops and eateries to theaters and art galleries, our campus fosters a vibrant student community. Enjoy access to state-of-the-art studios, communal study spaces, and a comprehensive library, ensuring a conducive environment for academic and personal growth.</div><div><br></div><div>Discover Your Path at the University of Essex&nbsp;&nbsp;</div><div>Embark on your academic journey with confidence through Kaplan Pathways. Our degree preparation courses at the University of Essex International College pave the way for your transition to undergraduate studies. Explore our diverse range of programs and unlock your potential at the University of Essex.</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div>', 1, '2024-05-19 16:14:35', '2024-05-21 00:17:01'),
(11, 8, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 'uploads/custom-images/blogs/image-2024-05-19-09-22-09-2540.jpg', 'Top 5 Benefits of Choosing the University of Liverpool', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Hello! I\'m Tony, a recent graduate with a bachelor’s degree in Law from the University of Liverpool. My time at university was truly incredible, and I\'m eager to share why Liverpool should be your top choice too. Here are my five compelling reasons:</span><br></p><p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">1. **Vibrant and Welcoming City**&nbsp;&nbsp;</b><br></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;Liverpool, voted the 4th friendliest city in the world by Rough Guide, offers a warm and diverse community. Immerse yourself in its rich culture through numerous galleries and museums. Plus, living costs are remarkably affordable.</p><p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">2. **Global Study Opportunities**&nbsp;&nbsp;</b><br></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;Experience international education firsthand with study abroad programs in China, Singapore, and beyond. Expand your horizons with language learning options and benefit from a robust global mentoring network.</p><p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">3. **Exceptional Career Support**&nbsp;&nbsp;</b><br></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;The University of Liverpool\'s career and employability services are top-notch, aiding in your future prospects. Employers highly regard our graduates, with 88% securing employment or further study within 6 months post-graduation.</p><p><b>4. **Pioneering Research Environment**&nbsp;&nbsp;</b></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;Engage in cutting-edge research at Liverpool, where 81% of projects are rated world-leading or internationally excellent. Join groundbreaking initiatives in personalized medicine and advanced materials, fostering innovation and discovery.</p><p><b>5. **Comprehensive Support Services**&nbsp;&nbsp;</b></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;Access dedicated assistance for academic and personal needs, including essay-writing guidance, mental health support, and tailored assistance for international students. Benefit from student peer mentors who navigate university life alongside you.</p><p>Embark on Your Journey at the University of Liverpool&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>I\'m thrilled with my decision to study here, and I\'m confident you\'ll feel the same. Join me in experiencing the wonders of Liverpool. If you\'re an international student, consider starting with a pathway course at the University of Liverpool International College, just as I did. It\'s the perfect stepping stone to success.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', 1, '2024-05-19 16:20:51', '2024-05-19 16:43:36'),
(12, 10, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 'uploads/custom-images/blogs/image-2024-05-19-09-25-11-3470.jpg', 'University of Essex: Leading the Way in Biodiversity Conservation', '<p style=\"border: 0px solid rgb(227, 227, 227); --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(69,89,164,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-backdrop-hue-rotate: ; --tw-backdrop-invert: ; --tw-backdrop-opacity: ; --tw-backdrop-saturate: ; --tw-backdrop-sepia: ; --tw-contain-size: ; --tw-contain-layout: ; --tw-contain-paint: ; --tw-contain-style: ; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25em; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(13, 13, 13); font-family: Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">We\'re thrilled to celebrate the University of Essex\'s dedication to environmental stewardship, particularly in safeguarding local wildlife. Recently, the university achieved a prestigious gold award at the Hedgehog Friendly Campus Awards 2021–22, highlighting its commitment to protecting these charming yet endangered creatures.</p><p style=\"border: 0px solid rgb(227, 227, 227); --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(69,89,164,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-backdrop-hue-rotate: ; --tw-backdrop-invert: ; --tw-backdrop-opacity: ; --tw-backdrop-saturate: ; --tw-backdrop-sepia: ; --tw-contain-size: ; --tw-contain-layout: ; --tw-contain-paint: ; --tw-contain-style: ; margin: 1.25em 0px; color: rgb(13, 13, 13); font-family: Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Hedgehogs, beloved for their small stature and gentle demeanor, are facing alarming declines in the UK. Since the turn of the century, their numbers have plummeted by half, earning them a classification as \'vulnerable to extinction\' within the country. Urban development and agricultural practices have encroached upon their natural habitats, leaving them with insufficient food sources and shelter.</p><p style=\"border: 0px solid rgb(227, 227, 227); --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(69,89,164,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-backdrop-hue-rotate: ; --tw-backdrop-invert: ; --tw-backdrop-opacity: ; --tw-backdrop-saturate: ; --tw-backdrop-sepia: ; --tw-contain-size: ; --tw-contain-layout: ; --tw-contain-paint: ; --tw-contain-style: ; margin: 1.25em 0px; color: rgb(13, 13, 13); font-family: Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">In response, the University of Essex has undertaken commendable initiatives to support hedgehog conservation. Recognized by the British Hedgehog Preservation Society, the university\'s Colchester Campus earned gold accreditation for various measures implemented in recent years. These efforts include employing full-time litter pickers to maintain a clean campus, installing hedgehog boxes for shelter, launching awareness campaigns, and creating natural log piles to attract insects, a vital food source for hedgehogs.</p><p style=\"border: 0px solid rgb(227, 227, 227); --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(69,89,164,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-backdrop-hue-rotate: ; --tw-backdrop-invert: ; --tw-backdrop-opacity: ; --tw-backdrop-saturate: ; --tw-backdrop-sepia: ; --tw-contain-size: ; --tw-contain-layout: ; --tw-contain-paint: ; --tw-contain-style: ; margin: 1.25em 0px 0px; color: rgb(13, 13, 13); font-family: Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Moreover, the university\'s Colchester Campus boasts an impressive array of 18 distinct habitats, fostering a diverse ecosystem teeming with plant and animal species. These habitats, including rare acid grasslands found in locations such as Campus Farm, Hance Meadow, Hay Meadow, and Skipper’s Meadow, provide vital support for a multitude of pollinators and other rare insect and spider species. Through such endeavors, the University of Essex exemplifies its dedication to biodiversity conservation and environmental sustainability.</p><p style=\"border: 0px solid rgb(227, 227, 227); --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(69,89,164,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-backdrop-hue-rotate: ; --tw-backdrop-invert: ; --tw-backdrop-opacity: ; --tw-backdrop-saturate: ; --tw-backdrop-sepia: ; --tw-contain-size: ; --tw-contain-layout: ; --tw-contain-paint: ; --tw-contain-style: ; margin: 1.25em 0px 0px; color: rgb(13, 13, 13); font-family: Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><br></p><p style=\"border: 0px solid rgb(227, 227, 227); --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(69,89,164,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-backdrop-hue-rotate: ; --tw-backdrop-invert: ; --tw-backdrop-opacity: ; --tw-backdrop-saturate: ; --tw-backdrop-sepia: ; --tw-contain-size: ; --tw-contain-layout: ; --tw-contain-paint: ; --tw-contain-style: ; margin: 1.25em 0px 0px; color: rgb(13, 13, 13); font-family: Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><br></p>', 1, '2024-05-19 16:25:11', '2024-05-19 16:43:41'),
(13, 9, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 'uploads/custom-images/blogs/image-2024-05-19-09-29-14-8927.jpg', 'Realizing Professional Triumph: David Ramirez\'s MBA Experience at SSBM Geneva', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><b>Choosing SSBM Geneva was a decision fueled by several compelling factors.</b></span></p><p>Firstly, SSBM\'s esteemed reputation for delivering top-tier business education with a global outlook deeply resonated with me. The prospect of learning from a diverse and seasoned faculty, coupled with its robust network of international affiliations, promised a well-rounded educational journey. Moreover, SSBM\'s emphasis on practical learning and real-world applications perfectly aligned with my career aspirations in space exploration and technology advancement.</p><p>How did SSBM\'s academic program and faculty contribute to your pursuit of a career in the food and CPG industry?</p><p>The program\'s curriculum and the expertise of its faculty members equipped me with the requisite knowledge, skills, and practical insights crucial for thriving in this dynamic and rapidly evolving sector.</p><p>The academic program at SSBM provided a meticulously crafted blend of fundamental business principles and specialized courses directly pertinent to the food and technology industry. Modules such as \"Innovation Management\" and \"Digital Marketing Strategies\" offered a deep understanding of how technological advancements influence the food sector and strategies to leverage them for innovative solutions. Additionally, courses on supply chain management and market analysis offered a comprehensive perspective on the industry\'s operational dynamics.</p><p>The faculty at SSBM comprised seasoned professionals with diverse backgrounds, including experts with hands-on experience in the food and technology industry. Their invaluable insights during lectures, discussions, and individual interactions bridged the gap between theoretical concepts and practical applications. Learning about the latest industry trends, challenges, and opportunities directly from industry veterans enriched my educational experience.</p><p>One notable aspect of the program was the integration of practical projects and case studies. These initiatives often tasked us with analyzing real-life business scenarios in the food and technology sector, fostering critical thinking, problem-solving skills, and the ability to apply theoretical knowledge in real-world contexts. Furthermore, the collaborative nature of these projects mirrored the teamwork and interdisciplinary collaboration prevalent in the industry.</p><p>In summary, SSBM\'s academic program and faculty provided a solid foundation and practical insights to excel in the food technology and CPG industry. The program\'s curriculum, coupled with faculty expertise and an emphasis on practical learning, empowered me to confidently pursue and succeed in my chosen career path.</p><p>Can you cite any instances or projects at SSBM that facilitated the acquisition of new skills?</p><p>Certainly, here are examples of instances or projects at SSBM that fostered the development of new skills pertinent to the food and Consumer Packaged Goods (CPG) industry.</p><p>New Product Innovation Challenge: This project entailed creating a novel product concept for the food and CPG industry, fostering creativity and honing skills in market research, ideation, and product development.</p><p>Brand Revitalization Case Study: Analyzing and revitalizing struggling food or CPG brands honed skills in market analysis, brand management, and strategic planning.</p><p>Digital Marketing Campaign: Crafting a digital marketing campaign for a food or CPG product honed skills in digital marketing, social media strategy, data analysis, and effective communication.</p><p>Collaborative Industry Challenge: Collaborating with industry partners to address real-world challenges in the food and CPG sector honed problem-solving and teamwork skills while offering insights into industry dynamics.</p><p>These projects exemplify how SSBM\'s practical approach to education fosters a range of skills essential for success in the industry.</p><p>What key selling points or advice would you offer to aspiring students considering SSBM based on your experiences?</p><p>I wholeheartedly recommend SSBM to aspiring students committed to excelling in their careers. The program\'s global perspective, combined with a practical and hands-on approach to learning, offers a comprehensive education highly relevant to the modern business landscape. Leveraging the faculty\'s industry expertise and actively engaging with coursework and resources can maximize the SSBM experience, paving the way for success in the competitive food and CPG industry.\"</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', 1, '2024-05-19 16:28:25', '2024-05-19 16:43:50'),
(14, 9, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 'uploads/custom-images/blogs/image-2024-05-19-09-33-22-7708.jpg', 'Rohini Ghavari\'s DBA Student Journey', '<p>Navigating the realm of higher education marks a pivotal juncture in one\'s life, laden with choices that sculpt both academic and professional trajectories. For many, flexibility isn\'t merely a convenience but a prerequisite, a sentiment echoed by countless individuals endeavoring to harmonize personal, professional, and educational obligations. Tilda Svedberg, an alumna of the Bachelor of Business Administration program at the Swiss School of Business and Management (SSBM) Geneva, embodies this ethos, where flexibility, assistance, and a comprehensive educational approach converge to forge pathways to success.</p><p>What inspired your pursuit of the BBA program at SSBM Geneva?</p><p>Flexibility is paramount to me, and SSBM Geneva afforded me the opportunity to access courses and online resources, enabling me to commence and conclude my studies at my convenience. Thanks to SSBM Geneva, I\'ve had the freedom to work and travel concurrently with my studies. I eagerly anticipate furthering my education with SSBM Geneva and pursuing my MBA.</p><p>Could you share an overview of your journey at SSBM Geneva and how it has primed you for your career?</p><p>The support from the student advisor has been invaluable every step of the way. Engaging in online studies demands significant self-discipline and adept time management, skills I foresee utilizing extensively in my career.</p><p>What specific competencies or insights did you glean from the BBA program that have proven most advantageous?</p><p>The BBA program encompasses a diverse array of courses spanning Business Strategy, Change Management, and Entrepreneurship. Each course fosters critical thinking and deliberation of potential solutions, affording me a robust comprehension of the business landscape.</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">What guidance would you offer to prospective candidates contemplating the BBA program at the Swiss School of Business and Management Geneva?</span></p><p>A BBA serves as a sturdy foundation regardless of one\'s career aspirations. If you seek to deepen your understanding of Business Management, this program equips you with requisite skills. Upon completion, you\'ll possess a clearer perspective on the subject matter, empowering you to delve into areas aligned with your interests in your MBA journey.</p><p>Tilda\'s odyssey at SSBM Geneva epitomizes the transformative influence of education and the limitless opportunities awaiting those bold enough to seize them. With flexibility as her compass and knowledge as her beacon, Tilda stands ready to embark on the next phase of her expedition, poised to leave an indelible mark on the world.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', 1, '2024-05-19 16:33:00', '2024-05-19 16:43:58'),
(15, 9, 2, NULL, 0, 1, 'uploads/custom-images/blogs/image-2024-05-19-09-36-54-9862.jpg', 'Spotlight on Student Testimonial: Exploring AI\'s Impact in the Luxury Sector with SSBM!', '<p>Meet Karina Vazhitova, a dynamic researcher and industry professional currently making significant strides at the esteemed Christian Dior Couture.</p><p>Embarking on a transformative academic journey, Karina has seamlessly integrated her hands-on experience at Christian Dior Couture with her academic pursuits, culminating in a groundbreaking dissertation titled “AI and Data-Driven Brand Decisions: Influence on Competitive Advantage in the Luxury Goods Industry.“</p><p>Let\'s delve into her insights, experiences, and the captivating world where fashion, technology, and strategic decision-making intersect.</p><p>What inspired you to pursue a Doctor of Business Administration (DBA) program at SSBM?</p><p>The exceptional program at SSBM in Geneva immediately caught my attention with its perfect balance of high-quality study materials and practical insights that resonate deeply with my research aspirations. As a full-time working professional, I value the program\'s flexibility and self-paced structure, which allow me to seamlessly merge work and studies and maximize the experience.</p><p>What specific facets of the luxury goods industry motivated you to explore the relationship between AI, data-driven strategies, and competitive advantage?</p><p>The allure of the luxury goods industry has always captivated me, driving my passion for exploration in this dynamic field. In today’s rapidly evolving landscape, companies must continuously refine their strategies to maintain competitiveness. With technology reshaping consumer preferences and market dynamics, leveraging AI for insights and decision-making becomes imperative in staying ahead.</p><p>What advice would you offer to fellow students interested in delving into research at the intersection of AI and business strategy?</p><p>Embrace a multidisciplinary approach, merging AI with fundamental business principles. Stay abreast of emerging trends, participate in conferences and webinars, collaborate with experts, and nurture a curiosity to delve deeper into this ever-evolving intersection.</p><p>How has your tenure at Christian Dior Couture influenced your research?</p><p>Being the sole representative from SSBM selected for the esteemed Women@Dior x UNESCO program for the 2024-2025 cohort is a distinct honor. This exclusive mentoring initiative, with only 120 women globally chosen annually from premier educational backgrounds, mirrors my commitment to empowerment, enrichment, and contributing to a sustainable future.</p><p>My engagement with LVMH has provided invaluable insights, fueling my research endeavors. I am eager to continue learning from industry leaders and advancing my research pursuits.</p><p>How has the DBA program at SSBM contributed to your professional growth and career aspirations?</p><p>The SSBM DBA program has significantly enhanced my strategic thinking and leadership abilities, perfectly aligning with my career aspirations.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', 1, '2024-05-19 16:36:54', '2024-05-19 16:44:38');

